metadata.name: Code the Frog
metadata.description:
Infinity/1 dynamic NFT randomly renders on your device. Background generated with Perlin noise, and Pepe randomly chooses from 1 of 2618 variations. What Pepe will you see? If you don't like it just click/tap the picture it will generate again. Have a nice experience!

Notice: foundation.app doesn't support such kind of content.
